    <node id="OBL-0069">
      <data key="d2">obligation</data>
      <data key="d3">Accordingly, we focus on how a broker-dealer could establish a reasonable basis to
believe that a recommendation is in the best interest of its retail customer and does not place the
73 See generally Section II.C.2, Care Obligation.</data>
