customers and need not provide a disclosure particularized to a recommendation).</data>
      <data key="d4">Section 2</data>
    </node>
    <node id="OBL-0342">
      <data key="d2">obligation</data>
      <data key="d3">494 See, e.g., SIFMA August 2018 Letter (asking the Commission to clarify that the
Disclosure Obligation does not apply in contexts where there is an existing regime, such
