      <data key="d4">Section 206</data>
    </node>
    <node id="OBL-0433">
      <data key="d2">obligation</data>
      <data key="d3">As noted above, the Commission is also incorporating into the rule text that broker-
dealers must have a reasonable basis to believe that the recommendation “does not place the
603 See Chapman Letter;</data>
      <data key="d4">Section 206</data>
