all component obligations of Regulation Best Interest.</data>
      <data key="d4">Section IV</data>
    </node>
    <node id="OBL-0746">
      <data key="d2">obligation</data>
      <data key="d3">$375,732 is the estimate of amending the account
disclosure agreement by small broker-dealers pursuant to the record-making obligation of
