    </node>
    <node id="OBL-0910">
      <data key="d2">obligation</data>
      <data key="d3">In addition, the following definitions shall
apply for purposes of this section:
(1) Retail customer means a natural person, or the legal representative of such natural person,
who:
(i) Receives a recommendation of any securities transaction or investment strategy involving
securities from a broker, dealer, or a natural person who is an associated person of a broker or
dealer;</data>
      <data key="d4">Section 240</data>
    </node>
    <node id="OBL-0911">
      <data key="d2">obligation</data>
      <data key="d3">(ii) For purposes of this paragraph (a)(35), the neglect, refusal, or inability of the retail customer
to provide or update any information described in paragraph (a)(35)(i) of this section shall
excuse the broker, dealer, or associated person from obtaining that required information.</data>
      <data key="d4">Section 240</data>
    </node>
